//Lymph nodes

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Spine MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lymph nodes' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Cervical' checkbox is enabled
And 'Paraaortal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Aortocaval' checkbox is enabled
And 'Parailiacal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pre-sacral' checkbox is enabled

And 'Borderline enlarged LN with central fat hilus' radio button is enabled
And 'Lymphadenopathy' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Cervical' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Parailiacal' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pre-sacral' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Lymphadenopathy' radio button
Then 'Largest lymph node, SAD' input field is enabled
